edia.org/resource/David_Hayter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Hayter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chaz's threshold\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4109}, {\"ngram\": \"Ollie\", \"from\": 4138, \"to\": 4143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bigham has been a modern-day Graeme Obree, bucking the system and being shut out of British Cycling until he finally convinced them that aerodynamic advantages can go much, much farther than physiology, nutrition and training.\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4235, \"end\": 4247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Graeme_Obree\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Graeme Obree\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Graeme_Obree\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Graeme_Obree\"}, {\"begin\": 4290, \"end\": 4305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4212}, {\"ngram\": \"the system\", \"from\": 4257, \"to\": 4267}, {\"ngram\": \"aerodynamic advantages\", \"from\": 4343, \"to\": 4365}, {\"ngram\": \"physiology\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"nutrition\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4418}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 4423, \"to\": 4431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will leave his debut Olympic and his final Olympics, he confirmed, with the memory of a lifetime even if the medal was silver and not gold.\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his debut\", \"from\": 4448, \"to\": 4457}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic\", \"from\": 4458, \"to\": 4465}, {\"ngram\": \"his final Olympics\", \"from\": 4470, \"to\": 4488}, {\"ngram\": \"the memory\", \"from\": 4509, \"to\": 4519}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifetime\", \"from\": 4523, \"to\": 4533}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a pretty cool experience, I have got to admit.\", \"from\": 4578, \"to\": 4632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pretty cool experience\", \"from\": 4586, \"to\": 4610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You want to finish it off on a high.\", \"from\": 4633, \"to\": 4669, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a high\", \"from\": 4662, \"to\": 4668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not to say it's not high, but you can make one intent and the intent is to try and win.\", \"from\": 4670, \"to\": 4762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one intent\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4728}, {\"ngram\": \"the intent\", \"from\": 4733, \"to\": 4743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a shame to not do that, and for it to be so close...\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shame\", \"from\": 4768, \"to\": 4775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure we will pour over the numbers and probably find out where we probably could have won it but it's all if buts or maybes now.\", \"from\": 4821, \"to\": 4954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the numbers\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4860}, {\"ngram\": \"if buts\", \"from\": 4932, \"to\": 4939}, {\"ngram\": \"maybes\", \"from\": 4943, \"to\": 4949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a long old journey.\", \"from\": 4956, \"to\": 4986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long old journey\", \"from\": 4967, \"to\": 4985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And one I am very proud of - a story that I am looking forward to continuing to tell the future over beers and meals out - and to tell my son 'You were here and you saw me winning the Olympic silver medal'.\", \"from\": 4987, \"to\": 5193, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a story\", \"from\": 5016, \"to\": 5023}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 5072, \"to\": 5082}, {\"ngram\": \"beers\", \"from\": 5088, \"to\": 5093}, {\"ngram\": \"my son\", \"from\": 5122, \"to\": 5128}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic silver medal\", \"from\": 5167, \"to\": 5191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's pretty awesome and it's very unique.\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hopefully, I have one more race in me at the World Champs to try and finish it on a high, and unfinished business in the individual pursuit against Filippo Ganna.\", \"from\": 5237, \"to\": 5400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5386, \"end\": 5399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Filippo Ganna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filippo_Ganna\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one more race\", \"from\": 5256, \"to\": 5269}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Champs\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5295}, {\"ngram\": \"a high, and unfinished business\", \"from\": 5320, \"to\": 5351}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual pursuit\", \"from\": 5355, \"to\": 5377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's been pretty amazing.\", \"from\": 5401, \"to\": 5430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's a very unique way of approaching the sport and I think that in itself, there are a lot of things I want to show about STEM about dual careers and about approaching the sport differently and not just accepting the status quo.\", \"from\": 5431, \"to\": 5668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5562, \"end\": 5566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_in_STEM_fields\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.975414375968567e-16, \"text\": \"STEM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_in_STEM_fields\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women_in_STEM_fields\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very unique way\", \"from\": 5444, \"to\": 5461}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 5477, \"to\": 5486}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5525, \"to\": 5530}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 5534, \"to\": 5540}, {\"ngram\": \"dual careers\", \"from\": 5573, \"to\": 5585}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 5608, \"to\": 5617}, {\"ngram\": \"the status quo\", \"from\": 5653, \"to\": 5667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope I can be a bright light in that respect that there is many ways to achieve performance and you do not just have to go the trodden path - you can go about things your own way.\\\"\", \"from\": 5670, \"to\": 5853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bright light\", \"from\": 5687, \"to\": 5701}, {\"ngram\": \"that respect\", \"from\": 5705, \"to\": 5717}, {\"ngram\": \"many ways\", \"from\": 5732, \"to\": 5741}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 5753, \"to\": 5764}, {\"ngram\": \"the trodden path\", \"from\": 5796, \"to\": 5812}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 5832, \"to\": 5838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bigham has revealed he will not return to work for Ineos Grenadiers as part of their performance staff.\", \"from\": 5855, \"to\": 5958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bigham\", \"from\": 5855, \"to\": 5861}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 5897, \"to\": 5901}, {\"ngram\": \"Ineos Grenadiers\", \"from\": 5906, \"to\": 5922}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 5926, \"to\": 5930}, {\"ngram\": \"their performance staff\", \"from\": 5934, \"to\": 5957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is expected to join a rival WorldTour team.\", \"from\": 5959, \"to\": 6005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rival WorldTour team\", \"from\": 5982, \"to\": 6004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laura Weislo is aCyclingnewsveteran of 20 years.\", \"from\": 6007, \"to\": 6055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6007, \"end\": 6012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/X-23\", \"score\": 0.9999999999731699, \"rank\": 2.6936848636019644e-11, \"text\": \"Laura\", \"types\": [\"Q9507